g.text: Provides comprehensive tools for event management, including creation, viewing, editing, and management.
Supports user authentication, both anonymous and via email.
Enables user profile navigation and management.
Includes distinct interfaces for admins, attendees, and organizers, facilitating various interaction modes with events.
Empowers administrators to review and delete events and user profiles through interactive interfaces.
Offers an overview of events and profiles, allowing for detailed management actions, such as deletion.
Improves attendee interaction with events through detailed event information, registration, and notification access.
Enhances attendee engagement with event notifications, providing a navigable list and user profile access, despite lacking QR code sharing.
Represents and manages detailed event information including serialization for data transfer.
Integrates with Firebase Firestore for event data operations and utilizes LiveData for real-time UI updates.
